_sText:
the map has 64 spawn points,radar view, good fps,custom textures,3D skybox, custom sounds.this map it's the improved version of my cs1.6 map de_emir http://www.cstrike-planet.com/maps/2228-de_emir
Enjoy!

note: purposely I did not included many details and HDR lightning (I just hate them)

If you are skilled enough,you may climb on almost everything on this map,it is not a  "map bug" it is because I wanted to be so,adds realism.
Although it has 64 spawn points the it is best played on a maximum 40 players.
